==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Paleness
<hw>Pale"ness</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality or
condition of being pale; want of freshness or ruddiness; a sickly
whiteness; lack of color or luster; wanness.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The blood the virgin's cheek forsook;⟦br⟧
A livid <qex>paleness</qex> spreads o'er all her look.</q>
<rj><qau>Pope.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Palenque</ent>⟦br⟧
